pqstat 0.2.0
William Swartzendruber <wswartzendruber@gmail.com>
Determines a PQ stream's brightness characteristics for HLG conversion

USAGE:
    pqstat <INPUT-FILE> --height <PIXELS> --width <PIXELS>

FLAGS:
        --help       Prints help information
    -V, --version    Prints version information

OPTIONS:
    -h, --height <PIXELS>    Height of the input video stream
    -w, --width <PIXELS>     Width of the input video stream

ARGS:
    <INPUT-FILE>    Raw input video stream (PQ, BT.2020, RGB48LE); use - for STDIN

